• Home
  • About Us
  • FIRST
  • Robots
  • Sponsors

"Orion" - 2022 - RAPID REACT

  • 22-26-0 in official play in 2022
  • District Event Finalist York University Day 1
  • District Event Winner Windsor Essex Great Lakes Event Day 2

"D3V1L" - 2020 - Infinite Recharge (Canceled Season)

  • 6-6-0 in official play in 2020

"Chester" - 2019 - Destination: Deep Space

  • 23-19-1 in official play in 2019
  • Creativity Award sponsored by Xerox (Ryerson University Event)

"Dementor" - 2018 - Power Up

  • 38-31-0 overall in 2018
  • Innovation in Control Award (Durham College Event) 
  • Darwin Division – Detroit World Championships

"Turtle" - 2017 - Steamworks

  • 36-23-2 in official play and 39-28-2 overall in 2017
  • Team Spirit Award (Durham College Event)
  • Alliance 6 captain Ontario Provincial Championships 
  • Darwin Division – World Championships

2016 - Stronghold

  • 7-5-0 in official play in 2016

2015 - Recycle Rush

  • 08-1-1 in official play in 2015

2014 - Aerial Assist

  • 6-14-0 in official play in 2014
  • Rookie All-Star Award (Greater Toronto East Regional)
  • Curie Division – World Championships
